  <div class="call-to-action">
    <h3>Let's Connect</h3>
<p>
  I’m open to conversations with pharmacists and scientists moving into tech, teams building 
  healthcare or education software, and anyone interested in applied data, modeling, or learning 
  systems. I’m especially interested in roles and collaborations that value domain knowledge as 
  much as technical execution.
</p>
<p>
  Based in Zimbabwe and open to remote opportunities, collaborations, and thoughtful conversations.
</p>

  </div>
